h drugs." Med Lett Drugs Ther 37 (1995): 73-4[5] Maish WA, Hampton EM, Whitsett TL, Shepard JD, Lovallo WR "Influence of grapefruit juice on caffeine pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics." Pharmacotherapy 16 (1996): 1046-52', 1767365203);
